    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything really is just entropy and noise. i look at the stars and i don't see anything inspiring, i just see a massive, cold vacuum that doesn't care if we exist or not. it's exhausting to keep pretending there's some point to the struggle when there literally isn't.",
